Package: nimbleMacros
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2025-01-28
Title: Macros Generating 'nimble' Code for Linear Models
Authors@R: c(person("Ken", "Kellner", email="contact@kenkellner.com", 
                    role=c("cre","aut")),
             person("Perry", "de Valpine", role = "aut"),
